trans-unit.source: Wraps a [Target Element (MSBuild)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca).
trans-unit.target: 包装 [Target 元素 (MSBuild)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca)。

trans-unit.source: This is an immutable class.
trans-unit.target: 这是一个不可变的类。

trans-unit.source: Gets the location of the AfterTargets attribute.
trans-unit.target: 获取 AfterTargets 特性的位置。

trans-unit.source: Returns the AfterTargets attribute location.
trans-unit.target: 返回 AfterTargets 特性位置。

trans-unit.source: Gets the location of the BeforeTargets attribute.
trans-unit.target: 获取 BeforeTargets 特性的位置。

trans-unit.source: Returns the BeforeTargets attribute location.
trans-unit.target: 返回 BeforeTargets 特性位置。

trans-unit.source: Gets a list of the children of this target.
trans-unit.target: 获取此目标的子级的列表。

trans-unit.source: The build iterates through this to get each task to execute.
trans-unit.target: 生成将循环访问此列表来获得要执行的每个任务。

trans-unit.source: Returns a list of the children of this target.
trans-unit.target: 返回此目标的子级的列表。

trans-unit.source: This is an ordered collection.
trans-unit.target: 这是一个有序集合。

trans-unit.source: This is a read-only list; the ProjectTargetInstance class is immutable.
trans-unit.target: 这是只读的列表;ProjectTargetInstance 类是不可变。

trans-unit.source: This collection does not contain the OnError target references.
trans-unit.target: 此集合不包含 OnError 目标引用。

trans-unit.source: Gets the unevaluated Condition attribute of this target element.
trans-unit.target: 获取此目标元素的未计算的 Condition 特性。

trans-unit.source: Returns the Condition attribute value.
trans-unit.target: 返回 Condition 特性的值。

trans-unit.source: Returns an empty string if the attribute is not present.
trans-unit.target: 如果该特性不存在，则返回空字符串。

trans-unit.source: Gets the location of the Condition attribute.
trans-unit.target: 获取条件特性的位置。

trans-unit.source: Returns the Condition attribute location.
trans-unit.target: 返回条件特性位置。

trans-unit.source: Gets an unevaluated semicolon-delimited list of targets that this target depends on.
trans-unit.target: 获取此目标所依赖的目标的未计算列表（各项之间用分号分隔）。

trans-unit.source: Returns an unevaluated semicolon-delimited list of targets that this target depends on.
trans-unit.target: 返回此目标所依赖的目标的未计算列表（各项之间用分号分隔）。

trans-unit.source: Returns an empty string if this target depends on no other targets.
trans-unit.target: 如果此目标不依赖任何其他目标，则返回空字符串。

trans-unit.source: Gets the location of the DependsOnTargets attribute.
trans-unit.target: 获取 DependsOnTargets 特性的位置。

trans-unit.source: Returns the DependsOnTargets attribute location.
trans-unit.target: 返回 DependsOnTargets 特性位置。

trans-unit.source: Gets the full path to the file from which this target originated.
trans-unit.target: 获取此目标源自于的文件的完整路径。

trans-unit.source: Returns the full path to the file from which this target originated.
trans-unit.target: 返回此目标源自于的文件的完整路径。

trans-unit.source: Returns an empty string if this target originated in a project that was not loaded and has never been given a path.
trans-unit.target: 如果此目标源自于未加载且未曾给定路径的项目，则返回空字符串。

trans-unit.source: Gets the unevaluated inputs on this target element.
trans-unit.target: 获取此目标元素的未计算的输入。

trans-unit.source: Returns the unevaluated inputs on this target element.
trans-unit.target: 返回此目标元素的未计算的输入。

trans-unit.source: Returns an empty string if this target has no inputs.
trans-unit.target: 如果此目标没有输入，则返回空字符串。

trans-unit.source: Gets the location of the Inputs attribute.
trans-unit.target: 获取输入特性的位置。

trans-unit.source: Returns the Inputs attribute location.
trans-unit.target: 返回输入特性位置。

trans-unit.source: Gets an unevaluated condition which is used to delete duplicate outputs from this target.
trans-unit.target: 获取用于从此目标删除重复输出的未计算的条件。

trans-unit.source: Returns an unevaluated condition which is used to delete duplicate outputs from this target.
trans-unit.target: 返回用于从此目标删除重复输出的未计算的条件。

trans-unit.source: Returns an empty string if there is no condition.
trans-unit.target: 如果不存在任何条件，则返回空字符串。

trans-unit.source: Gets the location of the KeepDuplicateOutputs attribute.
trans-unit.target: 获取 KeepDuplicateOutputs 特性（如有）的位置，如果有。

trans-unit.source: Returns the KeepDuplicateOutputs attribute location.
trans-unit.target: 返回 KeepDuplicateOutputs 特性位置。

trans-unit.source: Gets the location of the element itself.
trans-unit.target: 获取元素自身的位置。

trans-unit.source: Returns the element location.
trans-unit.target: 返回元素位置。

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the target.
trans-unit.target: 获取目标的名称。

trans-unit.source: Returns the name of the target.
trans-unit.target: 返回目标的名称。

trans-unit.source: Gets a list of the children of this target that refer to OnError targets.
trans-unit.target: 获取此目标的引用 OnError 目标的子级的列表。

trans-unit.source: Gets a list of the children of this target that refer to OnError targets.
trans-unit.target: 获取此目标的引用 OnError 目标的子级的列表。

trans-unit.source: This is an ordered collection.
trans-unit.target: 这是一个有序集合。

trans-unit.source: This is a read-only list; the ProjectTargetInstance class is immutable.
trans-unit.target: 这是只读的列表;ProjectTargetInstance 类是不可变。

trans-unit.source: Gets the unevaluated outputs on this target element May be empty string.
trans-unit.target: 获取此目标元素的未计算的输出。可能为空字符串。

trans-unit.source: Returns the unevaluated outputs on this target element Returns an empty string if there are no outputs.
trans-unit.target: 返回此目标元素的未计算的输出。如果没有任何输出，则返回空字符串。

trans-unit.source: Gets the location of the Outputs attribute.
trans-unit.target: 获取输出特性的位置。

trans-unit.source: Returns the Outputs attribute location.
trans-unit.target: 返回输出特性位置。

trans-unit.source: Gets the unevaluated return values on the target element as a string.
trans-unit.target: 以字符串的形式获取目标元素的未计算的返回值。

trans-unit.source: Returns the unevaluated return values on the target element as a string.
trans-unit.target: 以字符串的形式返回目标元素的未计算的返回值。

trans-unit.source: Returns an empty string or null, if no return value is specified.
trans-unit.target: 如果未指定返回值，则返回空字符串或 null。

trans-unit.source: Gets the location of the Returns attribute.
trans-unit.target: 获取返回结果特性的位置。

trans-unit.source: Returns the Returns attribute location.
trans-unit.target: 返回返回特性位置。

trans-unit.source: Gets all the tasks that are immediate children of this target.
trans-unit.target: 获取此目标的所有直接子级任务。

trans-unit.source: Returns all the tasks that are immediate children of this target.
trans-unit.target: 返回此目标的所有直接子级任务。
